- All code examples must be runnable and tested before inclusion
- Each chapter must include both test files and implementation files
- All code blocks must have syntax highlighting appropriate to the language
- Terminal commands must use terminal-block styling, not code-block styling
- All external links must open in new tabs (target="_blank")
- Images and SVGs should be optimized for web delivery